Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:05.97,Game Text Left,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! \NWhat are you looking for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.57,0:00:05.98,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Non-player characters...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:09.98,Game Text Left,,0000,0000,0000,,Clerk \NHey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.73,0:00:09.50,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,People in the game that aren't players.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:09.97,Game Text Right,,0000,0000,0000,,Clerk \NWhat are you \Nlooking for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.61,0:00:13.07,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,They say only predetermined lines,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.71,0:00:13.45,Game Text Left G,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(217,187)}Welcome to the village of Arb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.80,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,have no personalities,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.09,0:00:15.66,Game Text Right Y,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(173,185)}Where's the inn?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:16.24,Game Text Left G,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(194,224)}Welcome to the village of Arb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:18.10,Default - margin,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and exist merely to fulfill their game roles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:18.20,Game Text Right Y,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(105,182)}Hey! \NYou're totally hot! \NI'm in love with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:18.99,Game Text Left G,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(237,1)}Welcome to the village of Arb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.28,0:00:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In{\i0} Elder Tale, {\i1}players are called adventurers,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.75,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and NPCs are known as People of the Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.56,0:00:32.47,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But after the Apocalypse, something changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.09,0:02:08.77,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,Serara, you're okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.68,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.68,0:02:12.44,Default,H,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:15.51,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm sorry I worried you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.51,0:02:16.93,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.56,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I really am safe now, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.56,0:02:24.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We went over the Lyport Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.87,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have griffons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.20,0:02:30.37,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:37.20,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I'm safe, I just feel kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:42.72,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.85,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now that she feels safe, you feel hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:51.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't blame it on someone else, stupid Naotsugu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.20,0:02:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:59.86,Title1,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1567,1)}Return to Akihabara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.39,0:02:58.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Return to Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.74,0:03:05.06,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So we're supposed to set these up ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:07.57,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu, spread out the ground sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.71,0:03:11.39,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Shiro, since when have you been into camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.39,0:03:13.63,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I once read about it in a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:19.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Though I'm sure in the real world, \Nit wouldn't be this easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.18,0:03:23.63,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You never know what'll come \Nin handy in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.59,0:03:29.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A wild deer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:33.02,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So there are animals that aren't monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.02,0:03:36.61,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,This is my time to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.80,0:03:41.40,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.64,0:03:43.54,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,We have a place to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:48.05,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If this were the game, we'd only \Nneed to log out and go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.05,0:03:51.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're here, we might as well \Nhave fun doing it the hard way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.72,0:03:52.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our food...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:03:59.92,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It looks so yummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:02.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't taste like anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Serara and Nyanta are late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:08.11,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Something smells!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.11,0:04:09.87,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:11.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.17,0:04:14.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The smell of cooked meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:22.73,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like our hungry campers could smell the food cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:26.86,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't know about tasteless meat, \Neven if it does smell good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.45,0:04:33.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:36.54,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is... I can't describe it! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.69,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The texture when you bite into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The delicious juices...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:42.72,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The sweetness of the fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:47.22,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Just the right amount of salt, \Nwith rosemary for a secret ingredient...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.09,0:04:49.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,This is, without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.29,Default,All,0000,0000,0000,,The taste of real food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Chief! More!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:57.44,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.69,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be in such a rush. There's plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.44,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But how...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.96,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:09.91,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare the ingredients, and pick the \Nitem you want from the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:15.34,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,And it will make you a food item that \Nlooks just like the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.34,0:05:18.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, exactly like the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:19.88,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't taste like anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.88,0:05:22.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from thinking of this \Nin terms of a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:28.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Ingredient items like fruits and vegetables \Ntaste like the real things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:33.84,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So just do what I've done here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make it from the menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:42.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare and cook the ingredients \Nwith your own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.84,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We tried that, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.84,0:05:47.70,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,But look...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.77,0:05:51.38,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:54.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Try to boil it, and it becomes a weird paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:56.58,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what we did, \Nnone of us could make anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:06:00.08,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So we thought that was the rule in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.52,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That happened because the person \Nwho made it wasn't a chef,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:08.64,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,or didn't have the requisite cooking level.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:09.84,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:11.40,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.40,0:06:14.50,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,My subclass is chef.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:15.09,HUD Big,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(176,1)}Nyanta \N{\fs24}Race/ Cat-man \NSwashbuckler, Lv. 90 \NSubclass \NChef Lv. 90
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.74,0:06:17.10,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:21.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then to make it for real, someone with \Nthe appropriate skill must do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.79,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:25.11,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, I've been thinking \Nof things in game terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:27.57,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:30.84,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Master Nyanta...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.84,0:06:32.07,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,M-Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:34.35,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to introduce myself properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.82,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.23,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My class is Assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:38.46,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm level 90.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:41.44,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You were splendid back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:42.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:45.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I was impressed by the way you fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:46.37,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.37,0:06:48.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't how you acted toward me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.55,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not, Morontsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.55,0:06:51.47,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't shorten it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:53.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Talltsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.82,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.30,0:06:58.10,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I see you have good companions, Shiroe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.25,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Serara...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.35,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:04.36,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not properly introducing myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:07.65,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Serara, with the Crescent Moon Alliance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:11.52,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still a novice druid, at level 19.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.52,0:07:13.63,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,My subclass is maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:15.18,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,A-And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:20.24,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for the trouble I caused \Nwith my poor healing skills!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.62,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:25.25,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.25,0:07:27.64,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,And, Shiroe, thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:31.97,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.97,0:07:36.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no... I didn't do anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:40.93,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe's always been easily embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.50,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess, Serara.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:46.41,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been told you're \Nthe third cutest in class,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.41,0:07:49.60,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,but you get more love letters than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:50.94,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:57.07,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, I kneed that rude man in the face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:08:00.00,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with the knees, and enough \Nafter-action reports!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.29,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,While I was at it, I confiscated his meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.32,0:08:07.89,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.89,0:08:09.81,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You ate too much, Pigtsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.98,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,So you two have known each other a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.98,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Nyanta and Shiroe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.80,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:21.39,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,When this was a game, \Nwe were all in the same group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:26.15,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,It was called the Debauchery Tea Party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.56,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:34.49,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about a legendary party that \Ncompleted many difficult quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:37.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,That was my lord and Master Nyanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.69,0:08:39.54,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.81,0:08:43.21,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Then you were all in the same guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.21,0:08:47.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a guild. More like a hangout.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:51.31,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Each of us was in a different guild, \Nand was quite different than the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.62,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,We had nothing in common.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:58.44,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,We just happened to enjoy adventuring together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:02.56,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,That explains it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.40,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,How my master and his friends have griffons,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.42,Default - italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a high-level quest reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.84,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,And the way they work so well together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:18.57,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I've fought with my lord several times.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:23.33,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't even approach that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.03,Default - italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,I must practice more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.00,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Akatsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:29.23,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.23,0:09:30.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:34.17,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,But just now, you told a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:39.90,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Naotsugu couldn't possibly have been \Na member of such a legendary party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.39,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:48.40,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,That said, we went many different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.71,0:09:51.37,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,We also had many friends. It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:54.60,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.79,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Nyanta is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:14.30,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,A handsome young man, \Nkind and always willing to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:18.30,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,No, I think he's older... \NA handsome middle-aged man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:22.04,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,But he's so in shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:25.34,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Next to him, I look kind of fat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.34,0:10:28.31,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,I am a little overweight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.01,Default - italics,Se,0000,0000,0000,,But! But!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:31.62,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,So obvious...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:35.34,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So she's after middle-aged guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:37.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,He just seems like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.06,0:10:38.94,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,All that meowing is annoying, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.01,0:10:41.47,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Serara has good taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.33,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,You feel the same way about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.91,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The master is a first-class swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.18,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,That said...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.92,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,Chief Nyanta is all right with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:55.38,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,My lord, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.50,0:11:01.51,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't a swordsman, but you \Nare very talented, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:05.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Are you trying to console me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.61,0:11:08.06,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:15.08,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,When you see her like this, \Nshe really does look young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:17.16,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,How old do you suppose she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:20.57,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, you can't tell by looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.89,0:11:23.74,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Just based on looks, you'd say \NAkatsuki was in elemen—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.66,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Middle school, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:31.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Which would make her the \Nsame age as those twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:33.45,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:35.92,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I ran into them when this was a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:40.68,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The girl was a shrine maiden, \Nand the boy was a samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.23,0:11:44.82,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Mister! Mister! Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.99,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,Um, may we ask something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.47,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,Question!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:53.58,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is too weak to heal \Nmy little brother's wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.58,0:11:55.94,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly, we should buy items.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:58.56,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know where they're sold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.56,0:12:00.39,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,I want skills, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.39,0:12:02.60,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,If you know where to get them, tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:05.60,Default - flashback,S,0000,0000,0000,,Is this your first day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:06.51,Default - flashback,M,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:07.70,Default - flashback,T,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:12.99,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Have you always been that nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:16.04,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it when people come to me \Nbecause they want something...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:19.88,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,But those two were beginners.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:22.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed to be having \Na great time adventuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.96,0:12:28.42,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,So I showed them the ropes for a while, \Nusing the Teacher System.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.42,0:12:30.31,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Teacher System?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:34.28,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,A system that lets high-level \Nplayers lower their levels
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to play with lower-leveled characters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:38.10,Green HUD,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,426)}Teacher System
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.80,0:12:39.49,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hardly anyone used it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:41.83,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:46.03,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,All your stats took a huge hit, \Neven if only temporarily...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:48.59,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you drop your level?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.91,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:55.60,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty smart, Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:58.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,And where are those two now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,On my Friend List.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.30,0:13:04.55,HUD1,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}Tohya \N\NMinori \N\NShigeru \N\NCrusty
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:04.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The sister is Minori, and her \Nyounger brother is Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.17,0:13:08.55,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I saw them after the Apocalypse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:10.97,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then they were caught up in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.96,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I was with them right up until it happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.35,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the next thing I knew, \NI was back in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.35,0:13:16.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And they were gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.15,0:13:20.27,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,I was also teleported, into an abandoned building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.55,0:13:25.07,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said something to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.07,0:13:27.28,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they've been having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.42,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm sure he had his reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:39.38,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We had our hands full.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:42.80,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt we had the energy to spare...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.20,0:13:46.76,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,351)}And when I saw them, they were both in a guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.96,0:13:48.32,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:50.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, they were level 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.60,0:13:53.15,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Now, they might be a little higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.15,0:13:56.27,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,If they're in a guild, they should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.10,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:02.40,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Was Minori cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.40,0:14:04.09,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.50,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In the real world, all I could hear was her voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.11,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,And when I saw her, I couldn't see her face.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:09.77,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.78,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell some things from the voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:13.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid pervert Naotsugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.69,0:14:15.66,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Better than being a closet pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.39,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up... You're making my tea taste bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:20.96,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So let's talk about which is better, \Nbeing closeted or open!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.80,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.22,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The rain clouds are closing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:37.03,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe, we should probably \Nfind some shelter soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:37.73,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:39.73,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In this zone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:43.06,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,I think there's a village past those woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.17,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.17,0:14:51.87,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,The south end of the Arb Highlands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:53.82,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.82,0:14:54.65,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.65,0:14:57.50,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been alone since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.75,0:15:01.25,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Without joining any guilds?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.70,0:15:05.25,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What about you? \NWhat happened with that guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.53,0:15:07.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,The Cat Food guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.86,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.86,0:15:15.35,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,A proud organization comprised \Nsolely of cat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.13,0:15:19.31,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,I loved sitting on the porch, \Nbut the house was getting old.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.31,0:15:21.27,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:26.07,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.57,0:15:29.34,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,But it couldn't handle the bad weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.97,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,so half the house caved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.95,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Then it basically disbanded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.95,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.24,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We're travelers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:42.46,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Could you put us up for the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:45.96,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my... Adventurers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's a rare sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:49.81,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:52.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the village of Arb.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.45,0:15:55.77,Default - italics,S,0000,0000,0000,,A non-player character? \NA Person of the Land?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.77,0:15:59.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Fedor. I'm the village ombudsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.60,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.41,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.41,0:16:05.36,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? So you have a name...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:12.43,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You may use this barn as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:13.60,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:16.03,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.03,0:16:18.68,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Move. We have to give everyone some.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.54,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:22.14,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a hearth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:24.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Right over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:27.60,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go prepare dinner, Nyanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:29.20,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Give me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.20,0:16:30.67,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,This is for my lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.52,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.92,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends are quite lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.18,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:39.83,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... So you're going to Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:40.83,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:44.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We People of the Land travel little.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.69,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hear tales of our \Ntravels, we have plenty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:49.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to hear them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:56.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there... Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.62,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:00.49,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.53,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:02.89,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:03.62,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.48,0:17:05.51,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Mischa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.51,0:17:06.50,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Ivan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.44,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Mischa and Ivan, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.44,0:17:09.62,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Good names!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.91,0:17:12.90,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:13.55,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,A ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:14.79,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.26,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Throw a shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.81,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.81,0:17:19.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.06,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,They're all kids—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.30,0:17:26.31,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're my grandchildren...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:29.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,When they were born, it was very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.64,0:17:31.07,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:32.67,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There was a blizzard outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:36.14,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,And their father had gone to the town market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I was the only man here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I carried their mother to the doctor, \Non the other side of the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.28,0:17:41.52,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.52,0:17:42.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:48.46,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,So even NPCs not part of events \Nhave that kind of a backstory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:52.71,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,The more I talk to them, \Nthe more human they seem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:54.91,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They are human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:18:01.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They have names... \NFamilies, feelings, and memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.53,0:18:05.61,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,We adventurers have powerful bodies,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and can revive, no matter how often we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.97,0:18:14.78,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, wouldn't that \Nmake us the abnormal ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.21,0:18:17.78,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.47,0:18:20.67,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,They live as one with the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.79,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,That's how they get their name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.39,0:18:28.42,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the Apocalypse, it seems \Nlike I've seen far more of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.06,0:18:33.48,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we just never noticed \Nwhen it was a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.00,0:18:35.30,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.05,0:18:39.12,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.12,0:18:41.80,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,We went around to some neighboring houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:45.18,Default,Ny,0000,0000,0000,,They were nice enough to sell us some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:46.78,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this great?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:49.10,Default,Se,0000,0000,0000,,Cheese! Sausage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:52.20,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't crafted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:53.69,Default,A,0000,0000,0000,,Then how?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:57.37,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,No, come to think of it, \Nthose are ingredient items.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.37,0:18:59.57,Default,N,0000,0000,0000,,Some strange parts are just like the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's butter and eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.69,0:19:05.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I bought salt in Susukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:08.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So we can make cookies. \NRight, Nyanta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.30,0:19:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:12.21,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.10,0:19:25.93,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:36.19,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.52,0:19:39.19,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get back before the triffids respawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.83,0:19:42.41,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Our healer was sent to the Cathedral...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.95,0:19:46.66,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, why do I have to babysit these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:48.66,Default,Sh,0000,0000,0000,,My luck sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:51.64,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.64,0:19:52.95,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:55.08,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I just feel kind of lightheaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:55.79,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:59.76,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Two of us died today because of that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:00.55,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:04.30,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I hate to say it, but it's because we're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.55,0:20:06.75,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My luck sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.75,0:20:09.19,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't hit our quota.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:11.55,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's because your levels are too low!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:17.50,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's because his level is \Ntoo high, so we stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.50,0:20:18.82,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:20.82,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.82,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,but he attracts all the enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:27.37,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,As the tank, drawing their attention is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:30.10,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,That's why our formation always falls apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.14,0:20:33.62,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.29,0:20:35.65,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:39.84,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he used that Teacher System thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:43.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop talking and walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:46.82,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, we're almost to Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:48.04,Default,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,We can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.19,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.55,0:20:59.02,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,After a while, those wounds will \Nheal on their own, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:02.07,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Every day is rough for you, Tohya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:04.53,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Minori?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.94,0:21:06.35,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,These injuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.03,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,I spend the whole day sewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.58,0:21:12.45,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,Why did we join this guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:14.65,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't do anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.65,0:21:17.69,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much we didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:21.70,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.70,0:21:23.13,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Show us what you've got.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:30.18,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're lucky...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:35.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're useless, but you can still \Nearn three meals a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:41.57,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,At a time like this, what would he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:43.90,Default,T,0000,0000,0000,,What would Shiroe do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.90,Default,Minori,0000,0000,0000,,Shiroe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:54.64,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:57.20,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. Don't screw up today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:21:58.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.20,0:22:01.71,Default,Mi,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Serara! I'm so glad you're all right! \NThanks, Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.71,0:22:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.72,0:22:04.72,Default,S,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You don't need to thank me, Mari.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.40,0:22:08.22,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... It must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.22,0:22:09.83,Default - italics,T,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shiroe!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.97,0:22:21.12,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:22.32,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:08.25,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,We returned to Akihabara,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.25,0:24:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which seemed to be regaining a measure of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.53,0:24:15.35,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,But it was a false peace, in which the \Npowerful stole from the weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.35,0:24:18.49,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Are there some who realize it, \Nbut can do nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.49,0:24:20.06,Default,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,Is Shiroe one of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.06,0:24:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can he do nothing but watch, \Nas the world becomes twisted?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.94,0:24:30.99,Title1,,0000,0000,0000,,Resolve
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.26,0:24:26.05,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.05,0:24:27.98,Default,Next time,0000,0000,0000,,This is our reality.
